          </div>
          <p class="text-white text-xs font-body mb-4">Full access from day one. No trial.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 flex-1">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red flex-shrink-0 text-sm">✓</span><span class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-body">Everything in Annual</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red flex-shrink-0 text-sm">✓</span><span class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-body">Coaches Section</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red flex-shrink-0 text-sm">✓</span><span class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-body">PDF Season Plans</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red flex-shrink-0 text-sm">✓</span><span class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-body">Advanced Team Training</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red flex-shrink-0 text-sm">✓</span><span class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-body">Pro Player Sessions</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red flex-shrink-0 text-sm">✓</span><span class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-body">Workshop Discounts</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red flex-shrink-0 text-sm">✓</span><span class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-body">Coaching Templates</span></li>
